# goPyServer
This is Python JSONRPC server which can accept RPC calls from fellow Python Scripts as well as Golang Programs.
info.name: goPyServer
info.summary: This project is an implementation of the JSON-RPC Server which can easily cross communicate with Golang Client using goPy client Library
